title: Ham Radio Book Set
description:
Ham Radio Book Set:

1. Arrl - Experimental Methods In Rf Design (only CD, not book)
2. ARRL VHF Digital Handbook, 2008
3. ARRL Basic Antennas, 2005
4. Fifty Years Of ARRL, 1965
5. Hints and Kinks for the Radio Amateur-1978
6. Hints and Kinks for the Radio Amateur-1992
7. Nifty E-Z Guide to D-STAR Operation, 2009
8. Now You're Talking - 2003 - ham radio - arrl
9. Pager Handbook for the Radio Amateur, 1998
10. PIC Programming for Beginners, 2010
11. QRP Classics - The Best QRP Projects from QST and the ARRL Handbook, 1990
12. Radar Transmitters, 1993
13. The Gunnplexer Cookbook, 1981
14. The Laser Experimenters Handbook, 1979
15. The Radio Amateurs Microwave Communications Handbook, 1985
16. The Spread Spectrum Source Book, 1997
17. W1FB Design Notebook, 1990
18. W1FB QRP Notebook, 1991
19. Wireless Digital Communications-Design and Theory, 1998

Enjoy, and if you like please buy the books.
